title: Cities.Skylines.Snowfall.Update.v1.5.0.incl.DLC-CODEX
description:
Cities: Skylines - Snowfall Update v1.5.0 (c) Paradox Interactive
Release Date: 08/2016 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Simulation

See patchlog inside
New DLC included: Match Day
For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/420610/

Extract
Run setup.exe and install (Installer shows wrong version)
Copy crack from CODEX dir to installdir
Play

You need the following release for this: Cities.Skylines.Snowfall-CODEX

General Notes:

Block the game's exe in your firewall to prevent the game from
trying to go online
If you install games to your systemdrive, it may be necessary
to run this game with admin privileges instead
